b/20121219094524/http://www.gaonchart.co.kr/main/section/online/download/list.gaon |archivedate=19 December 2012 }}</ref>\n| style=\"text-align:center;\"| 76\n|}\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2016)\n!Peak<br />position\n|-\n{{singlechart|Billboardrocksongs|4|artist=Coldplay|artistid=299516}}\n|}\n{{col-2}}\n\n===Year-end charts===\n{|class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n!Chart (2008)\n!Position\n|-\n|Australia (ARIA)<ref>{{cite web|title=2008 ARIA Singles Chart|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/Annual-Charts/2008/Singles-Chart|website=ARIA Charts|publisher=ARIA \u2013 Australian Recording Industry Association Ltd.|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|33\n|-\n|Austria (\u00d63 Austria Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Jahreshitparade Singles 2008|url=http://www.austriancharts.at/year.asp?cat=s&id=2008|website=Austrian Charts|publisher=Hung Medien|accessdate=20 March 2016|language=German}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|33\n|-\n|Belgium (Ultratop Flanders)<ref>{{cite web|title=Jaaroverzichten 2008|url=http://www.ultratop.be/nl/annual.asp?year=2008|website=Ultratop|publisher=Ultratop & Hung Medien|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|16\n|-\n|Belgium (Ultratop Wallonia)<ref>{{cite web|title=Rapports Annuels 2008|url=http://www.ultratop.be/fr/annual.asp?year=2008|website=Ultratop|publisher=Ultratop & Hung Medien|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=French}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|40\n|-\n|Canada (Canadian Hot 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/canadian-hot-100?begin=1&order=position|title=Canadian Hot 100 Year-End 2008|accessdate=2012-03-29}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|9\n|-\n|Europe (European Hot 100 Singles)<ref>{{cite web|title=European Hot 100 Singles - Year End 2008|url=http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/european-hot-100-singles|website=Billboard|publisher=Billboard|accessdate=19 March 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20151012055155/http://www.billboard.com/charts/year-end/2008/european-hot-100-singles|archivedate=12 October 2015}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|15\n|-\n|France (SNEP)<ref>{{cite web|title=Classement Singles - ann\u00e9e 2008|url=http://www.disqueenfrance.com/fr/page-259376.xml?year=2008|website=Disqueen France|publisher=GfK Entertainment|accessdate=25 March 2016|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120404175938/http://www.disqueenfrance.com/fr/page-259376.xml?year=2008|archivedate=4 April 2012|language=French}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|43\n|-\n|Germany (Official German Charts)<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 100 Single-Jahrescharts|url=https://www.offiziellecharts.de/charts/single-jahr/for-date-2008|website=Offizielle Deutsche Charts|publisher=GfK Entertainment|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=German}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|26\n|-\n|Ireland (IRMA)<ref>{{cite web|title=Best of singles 2008|url=http://www.irma.ie/best-of-singles|website=IRMA|publisher=IRMA \u2013 Irish Recorded Music Association|accessdate=19 March 2016}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|20\n|-\n|Netherlands (Dutch Top 40)<ref>{{cite web|title=Top 100-Jaaroverzicht van 2008|url=http://www.top40.nl/bijzondere-lijsten/top-100-jaaroverzichten/2008|website=Dutch Top 40|publisher=Stichting Nederlandse Top 40|accessdate=19 March 2016|language=Dutch}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|2\n|-\n|Netherlands (Single Top 100)<ref>{{cite web|url=https://dutchcharts.nl/jaaroverzichten.asp?year=2008&cat=s|title=Jaaroverzichten \u2013 Single 2008|publisher=MegaCharts|language=Dutch|accessdate=24 March 2020}}</ref>\n|style=\"text-align:center;\"|6\n|-\n|Sweden (Sverigetopplistan)<ref>{{cite web |title=\u00c5rslista Singlar - \u00c5r 2008 |url=http://www.sverigetopplistan.se/netdata/ghl002.mbr/lista?liid=43&dfom=20080101&newi=0&mode=list&navi=no&platform=Win32&browser=MSIE |website=Sverigetopplistan |publisher=Gramophone Suppliers Association |accessdate=25 March 2016 |archive